body:
Hmm, we do this already I think, with the comparable Go API:s... [Here](https://github.com/syncthing/syncthing/blob/master/internal/beacon/multicast.go#L23) we join the group when listening and [here](https://github.com/syncthing/syncthing/blob/master/internal/beacon/multicast.go#L62) we do the send on a specific interface.. 

```
[P56IO] 2015/04/02 10:22:21.751814 beacon.go:30: DEBUG: recv 56 bytes from 172.21.21.222:21025
[P56IO] 2015/04/02 10:22:21.751890 multicast.go:65: DEBUG: write udp: no route to host on write to {ff32::5222 21026 lo0}
